Usage: rkm [options] [command]

Research Knowledge Manager - Cognitive Knowledge Graph CLI

Options:
  -V, --version             output the version number
  --db <path>               Path to RuVector storage file (default:
                            "./ruvector.db")
  --data-dir <path>         Path to graph data directory (default: "./data")
  --dims <number>           Embedding dimensions (default: "384")
  --no-cognitive            Disable cognitive features (SONA/GNN)
  -h, --help                display help for command

Commands:
  ingest [options]          Ingest a file or directory of research outputs into
                            Cognitive Knowledge Graph
  query [options] <text>    Semantic query over stored research with optional
                            graph exploration
  search [options] <text>   Hybrid search combining vector similarity and graph
                            relationships
  graph [options] <cypher>  Query the knowledge graph using Cypher-like syntax
  route [options] <query>   Analyze query intent and suggest execution strategy
  context [options] <text>  Print a Claude-Flow-ready context block from
                            RuVector search results (copy/paste into prompts)
  status [options]          Show system capabilities, memory statistics, and
                            learning progress
  learn [options]           Trigger SONA learning from recorded trajectories
  help [command]            display help for command

=== RuVector Capabilities ===

Implementation: native
  Native: Yes
  WASM: No
  Version: 0.1.35

Modules:
  GNN (Graph Neural Network): Available
  Attention: Not Available
  SONA (Self-Optimizing): Available
